snippet.textDisplay:
I genuinely could not stop tearing up when Hobi said success is seeing the smiles on people’s faces. They care so much about what they do and they want others to feel loved, to feel happy. We don’t find that in artists these days.
Also, Zach, thank you so much for asking these questions — I could see that the boys genuinely found this interview insightful and fulfilling. They, as world-class artists, deserve to be treated like one and only Zach can pull it off. ♡
